'''Tusken Music''' is a [[Wikipedia:Music publisher|music publishing]] arm of [[Lucasfilm]] The company is affiliated with [[Wikipedia:ASCAP|ASCAP]], and its publishing is administered by Walt Disney Music Publishing.

It is named after the [[Tusken Raider]]s.

